or-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Enhanced Game Statistics on Steam Store Pages<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-44751d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"44751d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1479\" alt=\"Enhanced Game Statistics on Steam Store Pages\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1-650x366.webp 650w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/12_11zon-1.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cb9a2f5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cb9a2f5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Starting from version 2.2.7, users can view expanded statistics on Steam game pages. The following information is now available:<\/span><\/p><ul><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Total number of reviews, including hidden ones<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: This helps provide a more objective assessment of a game&#8217;s popularity. For example, this is crucial if reviews are region-specific or there is a trend of removing comments.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Last update date and a link to its description<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: This is particularly useful for multiplayer games, allowing you to quickly determine whether a project is actively supported.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Peak player counts over the past 24 hours and all-time peaks<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: This feature is invaluable for those who prefer online games with an active player base.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><b>Price history and lowest recorded price of a game<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: You no longer have to rely solely on Steam sales\u2014you can easily track price changes and buy games under the most favorable conditions.<\/span><\/li><\/ul><p><em><b>Practical Benefits<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">:<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> With these improvements, users can quickly assess whether a game is worth its price, whether it is actively updated, and how popular it currently is.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-79a3e4e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"79a3e4e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f288c90 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f288c90\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Notifications About Free Items<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6546eca elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6546eca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Another new feature is automatic notifications about free items. The extension checks for freebies every 24 hours and sends a notification directly to your browser. This is especially relevant for those collecting items like in-game skins, cards, or exclusive time-limited items.<\/span><\/p><p><em><b>Use Case Example<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can set up notifications to receive timely information about giveaways, helping you expand your collection without additional costs.<\/span><\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a0e24a7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a0e24a7\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ccdb91d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ccdb91d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">New Tools for Managing Inventory<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-105fea6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"105fea6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/23141234_11zon-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1484\" alt=\"New Tools for Managing Inventory\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/23141234_11zon-1024x576.webp 1024w, https: