iv class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9e72797 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"9e72797\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Additional Information on Item Pages<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-857ba7f elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"857ba7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-1478\" alt=\"Additional Information on Item Pages\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7-1024x576.webp 1024w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7-1536x864.webp 1536w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7-650x366.webp 650w, https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/4_11zon-7.webp 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e9a0eef elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e9a0eef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the most useful additions in version 2.2.10 is the ability to see which case an item comes from (available after clicking the &#8220;Show more info&#8221; button). This feature is extremely beneficial for collectors and traders who buy or actively open cases.<\/span><\/p><p><b><i>Why This Matters<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">: <\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Knowing an item\u2019s origin allows for a more accurate evaluation of its value, particularly for rare or limited collections. For example, some items are produced in limited quantities, and information about the case or collection can influence purchasing decisions. This is also relevant when selecting items as long-term investments or those that may soon be removed from the in-game store.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Additionally, a new feature tracks active buy orders while promoting items to the top. This helps avoid errors when listing offers and enables more profitable deals.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4b1fee3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4b1fee3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0b6e12 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f0b6e12\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Currency Conversion on SIH.Market<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce5c98b elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ce5c98b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"563\" src=\"https:\/\/blog.sih.app\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/2_11zon-6-1024x576.webp\" class=\"attachment-lar