><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Fixed issues with weapon pattern displays, making it easier to search for rare items.<\/span><\/li><li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Resolved bugs in the trade window, ensuring proper display of game subsections.<\/span><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-df26399 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"df26399\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-39bda78 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"39bda78\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a5b2369 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a5b2369\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Steam Inventory Helper strives to make the extension as convenient as possible for all user categories. From enhanced game statistics to new tools for traders, there\u2019s something useful for everyone.<\/span><\/em><\/p><p><em><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Stay updated with SIH to keep track of the latest features and be among the first to take advantage of them!<\/span><\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>The developers of Steam Inventory Helper continue to actively improve the extension, adding useful featur